HEADWORD: Polygyny
<hw>Po*lyg"y*ny</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Poly-</ets>
+ Gr. <?/ woman, wife.]</ety> <def>The state or practice of having
several wives at the same time; marriage to several wives.</def>
